  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Persistent esophagitis

          -  Heartburn

          -  Nausea

          -  Vomiting

          -  Severe dyspepsia

          -  Severe chronic constipation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of, or current arrhythmias including ventricular tachycardia,   - Ventricular
             fibrillation and Torsade des Pointes.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
